channel.title: [REL] Cheat Client
channel.description:
Credits to: L33tdefisawesome and the maker of DDsSpeczV8 remake of Roatpkz. All I take credit for is putting one and two together to make a cheat client, and a little bit of java decompiling and fixing errors.
To use this client, you must know how to find the uid of a server, ip address, port, and modifying npc bits client sided. I've tested it on multiple severs that I could grasp the server information from, any who enjoy.
Place the cache in the "C:" location. Link: http://up.ht/1a9JezD
Here are the client files to run it. Link: http://up.ht/1g6vIoZ
Bon Appétit, and a thank-you comment wouldn't hurt if you're using.
